{"tid":748771,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐戰之巔猛將篇】C朗：留皇馬到40歲！","createTime":"2018-07-19T12:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T13:36:31.000Z","uid":53062,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"601f49dc48d49ed444adf990dac9fdfc8451d5e3","tid":748771,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/7/297/18169995297/18178554349_589x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F7%2F297%2F18169995297%2F18178554349_589x420.jpg&h=1345b8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=76a7ad46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度，又再表露思念英超之情，但同時又向這支西甲勁旅派定心丸，聲稱至少踢到40歲才離開。<br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）曾效力曼聯6個球季，直至2009年才以天價轉會費過檔皇馬，最近被西班牙電視台問及他關於今季遭自家球迷柴台的感受，再次表示想念曼聯及英超的球迷。<br />\n<br />\n「或許在這裡，球迷噓自己球隊很正常，但我就是不喜歡。」C朗坦言，「一名球員給出100%的努力，當他只犯了第一個錯誤，就被球迷噓，那是不正確的，不應如此。我在曼聯踢了好幾年，球迷從來沒有這樣對我，或許英格蘭是一個特別的例子。我在西班牙很快樂，但我也很想念英格蘭，因為那些回憶是不能刪除的。」<br />\n<br />\nC朗下季即將33歲，但他堅稱自己仍可以在皇馬留多7年：「41歲！當我上次簽約時，我就說這會是我倒數第2次續約，我會一直踢，41歲才轉會。」"},{"pid":"aa18d74c7c64e3c442d9030052dfa658f017a4e7","tid":748771,"uid":18279,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"皇馬一向唔係球員話事"},{"pid":"368f4a686b864765f3a62f42a9e11a7405aad9ae","tid":748771,"uid":60506,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"Haha Madrid"},{"pid":"c49291dbff5f1419c8a3c5e56c1e91d09f3a60ec","tid":748771,"uid":67444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9648fc0b90ed25552ae3cb619bb4bd8efaaa55ac","tid":748771,"uid":29993,"lik